<view class="user-page"><view class="card auth-card"><view class="auth-status"><text class="auth-status-label">当前认证状态：</text><text class="{{['auth-status-value', b]}}">{{a}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{c}}" class="loading-panel"><text class="loading-text">加载认证状态中...</text></view><view wx:elif="{{d}}" class="passed-panel"><view class="passed-title">学生认证信息</view><view class="passed-row"><text class="passed-label">学校</text><text class="passed-value">{{e}}</text></view><view class="passed-row"><text class="passed-label">学号</text><text class="passed-value">{{f}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{g}}" class="passed-row"><text class="passed-label">邮箱</text><text class="passed-value">{{h}}</text></view><view class="tip-text">如信息有误，请联系管理员处理。</view></view><view wx:else><view class="mode-tabs"><text class="{{['mode-tab', i && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{j}}">学生邮箱认证</text><text class="{{['mode-tab', k && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{l}}">材料上传认证</text></view><view wx:if="{{m}}"><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">学校名称</text><input class="form-input" placeholder="例如 华东师范大学" value="{{n}}" bindinput="{{o}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">学生邮箱</text><input class="form-input" placeholder="例如 xxx@stu.ecnu.edu.cn" value="{{p}}" bindinput="{{q}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">验证码</text><view class="code-row"><input class="form-input code-input" placeholder="6位验证码" maxlength="6" value="{{r}}" bindinput="{{s}}"/><button class="code-btn" disabled="{{v}}" bindtap="{{w}}">{{t}}</button></view></view><view class="tip-text">仅支持以 <text class="mono">.edu.cn</text> 结尾的学生邮箱。</view><button class="btn btn-primary" disabled="{{y}}" bindtap="{{z}}">{{x}}</button></view><view wx:else><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">姓名</text><input class="form-input" placeholder="请输入真实姓名" value="{{A}}" bindinput="{{B}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">学号</text><input class="form-input" placeholder="请输入学号" value="{{C}}" bindinput="{{D}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">专业</text><input class="form-input" placeholder="例如 计算机科学与技术" value="{{E}}" bindinput="{{F}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">年级</text><input class="form-input" placeholder="例如 2022级" value="{{G}}" bindinput="{{H}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">校园邮箱</text><input class="form-input" placeholder="例如 xxx@stu.ecnu.cn" value="{{I}}" bindinput="{{J}}"/></view><view class="form-item"><text class="form-label">认证材料（可多张）</text><view class="upload-row"><button class="upload-btn" disabled="{{K}}" bindtap="{{L}}">选择并上传</button><text wx:if="{{M}}" class="upload-tip">上传中...</text></view><view wx:if="{{N}}" class="file-list"><view wx:for="{{O}}" wx:for-item="f" wx:key="c" class="file-item"><text class="file-name">{{f.a}}</text><text class="file-del" bindtap="{{f.b}}">删除</text></view></view><view class="tip-text">材料将上传到后端并用于人工审核。</view></view><view class="tip-text">以上信息仅用于校内身份核验，不会对外展示。</view><button class="btn btn-primary" disabled="{{Q}}" bindtap="{{R}}">{{P}}</button></view></view></view></view>